<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weather</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-+0n0xVW2eSR5OomGNYDnhzAbDsOXxcvSN1TPprVMTNDbiYZCxYbOOl7+AMvyTG2x" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="310x310" href="/img/favicons/ms-icon-310x310.png">
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
</head>
<style>
    .img-box{
        overflow: hidden;
        display: inline-block;
        height: 10%;
    }
    .img-box img{
        width: 80%;
        transform: translate(0,-5%);
    }
    .details p{
        text-align: justify;
        margin: 0px;
    }
    .about-info{
        height: 60vh;
    }
 
</style>

<body>
    <div class="container-fluid main">
        {{>header}}
        <div class="about-info m-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="img-box text-end col-2 me-4 p-0">
                    <img src="img/my-image.jpg" alt="Creator Image">
                </div>
                <div class="text-white details p-3 col">
                   <h2>Dhananjay Gore</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4">This application is made with Node js and it is responsive thanks to Bootstrap. It uses API from www.weatherapi.com for getting weather details and
                         www.mapbox.com for getting Geo location and Map services. This application provides Real-Time weather details along with current day Analytics.
                        It also provides weather forecast of next 2 days, focusing on whether there will be rain or not and also astronomy of sunrise and sunset.
                        It shows highest temperature and chance of rain in percentage.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{>footer}}
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-gtEjrD/SeCtmISkJkNUaaKMoLD0//ElJ19smozuHV6z3Iehds+3Ulb9Bn9Plx0x4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>